%% Diagram: Spotify Connect playback handoff
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Phone as Phone (active)
    participant ZC as Local network (mDNS / ZeroConf)
    participant Speaker as Smart speaker (Connect SDK)
    participant API as Spotify Web API
    participant Backend as Player state service
    participant CDN as Audio CDN

    Phone->>ZC: Browse for _spotify-connect._tcp services
    Speaker-->>ZC: Advertise device + capabilities
    ZC-->>Phone: Discovered speaker
    Phone->>Speaker: ZeroConf addUser (credentials, blob)
    Speaker->>Backend: Register device, fetch player state
    Backend-->>Speaker: Current track, position, queue, volume
    Phone->>API: PUT /me/player {device_ids:[speaker]}
    API->>Backend: Transfer active device
    Backend-->>Phone: kSpPlaybackNotifyBecameInactive
    Backend-->>Speaker: kSpPlaybackNotifyBecameActive
    Speaker->>CDN: GET signed audio segment URL
    CDN-->>Speaker: Audio bytes
    Speaker->>Backend: Heartbeat (position, buffer health)
    Phone->>API: PUT /me/player/volume?volume_percent=N
    API-->>Speaker: SpCallbackPlaybackApplyVolume
